      "effect": "During your Main Phase: You can add 1 \"Witchcrafter\" monster from your Deck to your hand, then discard 1 card. You can only use this effect of \"Witchcrafter Walpurgis\" once per turn. During your turn, if you would discard to activate the effect of a \"Witchcrafter\" monster you control, you can send 1 \"Witchcrafter\" Spell/Trap from your Deck to the GY instead, except \"Witchcrafter Walpurgis\".",
